{
  "chapter": 31,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十回 关外雅士。沈浪与染香在快活林中周旋，识破春娇的阴谋。春娇企图借快活王之手除掉沈浪，沈浪将计就计，故意暴露身份引快活王前来。急风骑士前来试探，被沈浪轻松击败。快活王门下送来赌局请帖，沈浪准备与快活王展开一场豪赌。各路豪门巨富陆续抵达，为赌局增添紧张气氛。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？……嗯……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她如此做法，只是要将白飞飞送入快活王手里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你现在已完全懂了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可怜白飞飞，她本是个纯洁的女孩子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你喜欢她？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不能喜欢她？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能……能……能……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你猜猜看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我相信你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_ming_qin",
      "speaker_name": "楚鸣琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下却非酒徒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "楚兄既不喝酒，为何要调酒？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他本来就是个妙人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "她突然轻哼一声，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真可惜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可惜什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你为何……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好我未真个娶你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小鬼……小鬼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞧什么？没瞧过？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_ming_qin",
      "speaker_name": "楚鸣琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "的确没瞧过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_ming_qin",
      "speaker_name": "楚鸣琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但直到今日，我才认清楚你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你今天可是吃了冰，怎的说话老是带着冰碴子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_ming_qin",
      "speaker_name": "楚鸣琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我问你，只要是男人，你就对他有兴趣么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_ming_qin",
      "speaker_name": "楚鸣琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为我？哼！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_ming_qin",
      "speaker_name": "楚鸣琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要替人戴帽子时，理由总有不少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你只管放心，姓沈的已被染香那骚丫头缠得紧紧的，我就算是想要下手，可也没法子……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_ming_qin",
      "speaker_name": "楚鸣琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你失望得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好我一计不成，还有二计。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_ming_qin",
      "speaker_name": "楚鸣琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你还能强拉他不成。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我却可以杀了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_ming_qin",
      "speaker_name": "楚鸣琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀了他，你敢？若是被王夫人知道，你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我自不会自己动手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_ming_qin",
      "speaker_name": "楚鸣琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你也休想要我动手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……我做梦都未想到你会杀人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_ming_qin",
      "speaker_name": "楚鸣琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想到要谁杀人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你莫非忘了明天谁要来么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_ming_qin",
      "speaker_name": "楚鸣琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是说……快活王？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_ming_qin",
      "speaker_name": "楚鸣琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快……快活王又怎会杀他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非但不能娶老婆，简直连女人都莫要接近最好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？女人又不是毒蛇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女人虽不是毒蛇，但却都是怪物。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怪物？女人有什么奇怪之处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你方才撞了鬼么？回来说这些鬼话！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我方才虽未撞见鬼，却听见一段有趣的鬼话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "他淡淡一笑，接",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只不过听见有人想杀我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "春娇？这婆娘疯了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我倒要看看她有什么法子杀你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她自然不会自己下手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁下手都没关系，反正……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快活王下手又如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快活王？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快活王明天就要来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要去哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去哪里？自然是先去宰了她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不杀她，难道还等她破坏咱们的大事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她什么事也破坏不了的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她有法子，难道我没法子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你有什么法子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我正想不知该如何才能接近快活王，此番正要将计就计……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说呀，接着说呀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能说了，天机不可泄漏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来得倒真早。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "其中一人仿佛厉声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "两人齐声喝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "急风骑士，果然英俊。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "那第七骑士厉声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位若要找人，想必就是找我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "急风第八骑士厉声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你就是要找我家王爷的人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "那两人又交换了个眼色，齐声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "他微微一笑，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此厚赐，担当不起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "急风十三式，果然有些门道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好小子，倒真有种。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还要再打么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "急风骑士对望一眼，突然齐声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不打了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然不打，就回去吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "急风骑土",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们回去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "急风骑士嘶声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你，你为何出手拦阻？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不胜则死，快活王门下果然傲骨如钢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "急风骑士厉声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "剑在人在，剑折人亡，此乃本门规矩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "急风骑士再次对望一眼，大声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，沈浪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么多天来，你还不知道我本是死人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死人……死人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你简直连死人都不是，你……根本不是人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他，他真的要来了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来的只怕比预期中还要快。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他门下的急风骑士，我方才已见过了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想她说了没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她怎么说的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若想要快活王杀我，你会在他面前说什么话？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她竟真的这样说了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不说也是白不说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这恶婆娘……快活王门下听了这话，怎会放过你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他为何要杀我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听见了又怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪和快活王作对，天下谁不知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我正是要他知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你疯了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你……他却决不会收买你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他必定知道你是买不动的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……这……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行，这样做太冒险。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对付这样的人，不冒险行么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也知道对付非常之人，要用非常的手段，但是你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不必为我担心，我死不了的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能被美女如此怀恨，倒真是件值得开心得意之事，只可惜世上大多男人，都享受不到这滋味……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我只是来瞧瞧……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞧什么？是否瞧我死了没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈……沈公子说笑了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咳咳……沈公子……香姑娘昨夜睡得好么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是是是，我真该走了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "春娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，好，没问题。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人好大的气派。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非是快活王来了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不是快活王是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shui",
      "speaker_name": "春水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说出来香姑娘也不会认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不妨说来听听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shui",
      "speaker_name": "春水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人姓郑，别人都叫他郑兰州。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 694
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shui",
      "speaker_name": "春水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他家的金子，的确是太多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 708
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人又是何身份？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 710
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然是个暴发户。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪我远远就闻着铜臭气了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 718
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shui",
      "speaker_name": "春水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但他可不像猴子，倒像个猩猩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 724
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来只怕还有人来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 728,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shui",
      "speaker_name": "春水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天中午起码有六七起人要来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 730
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？还有什么人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 732
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shui",
      "speaker_name": "春水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然不是豪门，就是巨富，譬如说……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这也算豪门巨富么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 740,
      "line_end": 740
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一条汉子，这气概真有几分和猫儿相似了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 752
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shui",
      "speaker_name": "春水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "猫儿？他可不是猫儿，他是龙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 754,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龙？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 756
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦，此人又是何身份？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些却是什么人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 806,
      "line_end": 806
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是个败家子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 822,
      "line_end": 822
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shui",
      "speaker_name": "春水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些人全是被快活王约来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 832,
      "line_end": 832
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦！这些人和快活王有何关系？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 834,
      "line_end": 834
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来，我是少不得也要参加一份的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 848,
      "line_end": 848
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快活王来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 856,
      "line_end": 856
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，此人一来，果然吵得天翻地覆。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 858,
      "line_end": 858
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱……咱们怎么办？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 860,
      "line_end": 860
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等着吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 862,
      "line_end": 862
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等着，就……这样等着？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 864,
      "line_end": 864
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还怕他不来找我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 866,
      "line_end": 866
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "养足了精神，才能去对付快活王。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 878,
      "line_end": 878
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你要和他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 880,
      "line_end": 880
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但……但你现在……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 886,
      "line_end": 886
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你有胜他的把握？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 908,
      "line_end": 908
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 910,
      "line_end": 910
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎知我不紧张，不着急？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 916,
      "line_end": 916
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但……但至少我瞧不出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 918,
      "line_end": 918
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不想你非但是色狼，是酒鬼，还是个赌棍。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 924,
      "line_end": 924
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "突听门外一人沉声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪沈公子可是住在这里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 926,
      "line_end": 926
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 928,
      "line_end": 928
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是，足下莫非是快活王门下使者？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 934,
      "line_end": 934
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有劳兄台了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 944,
      "line_end": 944
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "锦衣少年面目微变，倒退三步，躬身",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈公子果然不凡。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 948,
      "line_end": 948
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "过奖，过奖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 950,
      "line_end": 950
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我此刻更要好好养养神了，你可千万莫要吵我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 970,
      "line_end": 970
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "总有一半把握吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 998,
      "line_end": 998
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大概总是有的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1000,
      "line_end": 1000
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谢谢老天……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1002,
      "line_end": 1002
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "早知如此，该多带些来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1008,
      "line_end": 1008
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那也没什么。我只要不让快活王猜出我赌本究竟有多少，他也就不敢全力出击的，何况……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1010,
      "line_end": 1010
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢，但……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1086,
      "line_end": 1086
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下沉浪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1104,
      "line_end": 1104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yuan_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "夏沅沅",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪，不错，我瞧你很有意思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1106,
      "line_end": 1106
    }
